37 registration fee of the vehicle registered hereunder under this section, plus
38 the regular fee prescribed by law for certificate of title. If any truck or
39 truck tractor which that is registered under the provisions of this
40 subsection section is exchanged or traded by the owner thereof for another
41 truck or truck tractor, any registration fee and any quarterly installments
42 which that have been paid shall be applied to the registration fee due for
43 the registration of the newly acquired vehicle. The application of any such

